@174  = ~Raasi'doch de Velle spent many moons working with the artisans of the Wandering Village in the creation of this enchanted hunter's spear. The elven ranger needed a weapon to exterminate werewolves terrorizing Tethyr's woods. Like the man himself, though the weapon is bereft of extravagant ornamentation it always flies straight and true.  When the crusade was finished he probably sold his inventory some famous militarist.

