@177  = ~Questing Staff +3~
@178  = ~Questing staves were originally created in some other realm, but they have found their way to Faerun. They are usually filled with spells that provide some protection, or entrance or egress, or grant simple knowledge, as well as provide warding against certain elements. This particular staff casts Knock, Ghost Armor, Detect Evil, Cure Critical Wounds, and Raise Dead, each upon command, and without limit. Moreover, it provides protection from fire like the ring of that name and some resistance against magic.

